":56},\"Answer\",\"text\",\"Local and State sales tax will be collected if your recipient's mailing address is in: \u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eArizona\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eCalifornia\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eColorado\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\",\"When will my credit card be charged?\",{\"_41\":54,\"_55\":59},\"We'll attempt to securely charge your credit card at the point of purchase online. If there's a problem, you'll be notified on the spot and prompted to use another card. Once we receive verification of sufficient funds, your payment will be completed and transferred securely to us. Your account will be charged in 24 to 48 hours.\",\"What is the policy for late/non-delivery of items ordered online?\",{\"_41\":54,\"_55\":62},\"\u003cp\u003eOur local teams work diligently to make sure that your order arrives on time, within our normaldelivery hours of 9AM to 8PM in the recipient's time zone. During  busy holiday periods like Christmas, Valentine's and Mother's Day, we may extend our delivery hours before 9AM and after 8PM to ensure that all gifts are delivered on time. If for any reason your gift does not arrive on time, our dedicated Customer Service agents will do everything they can to help successfully resolve your issue.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=https://example.com/orders/\u003eClick here\u003c/a\u003e to complete the form with your order-related question(s).\u003c/p\u003e\",\"How long does it take to process a refund?\",{\"_41\":54,\"_55\":65},\"We will reimburse you for returned items in the same way you paid for them. For example, any amounts deducted from a gift card will be credited back to a gift card. For returns by mail, once we receive your return, we will process it within 4–5 business days. It may take up to 7 days after we process the return to reflect in your account, depending on your financial institution's processing time.\",\"What is the return policy?\",{\"_41\":54,\"_55\":68},\"\u003cp\u003eMost unopened items in new condition and returned within \u003cb\u003e90 days\u003c/b\u003e will receive a refund or exchange. Some items have a modified return policy noted on the receipt or packing slip. Items that are opened or damaged or do not have a receipt may be denied a refund or exchange. Items purchased online or in-store may be returned to any store.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eOnline purchases may be returned via a major parcel carrier. \u003ca href=http://example.com/returns\u003e Click here \u003c/a\u003e to initiate a return.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"meta\",{\"_93\":72,\"_17\":94,\"_95\":96,\"_97\":98},\"page_title\",\"HealthifyMe - Track Nutrition, Plan Your Diet, Get Fitter\",\"app_link\",{\"_83\":84,\"_85\":86},\"logo\",{\"_77\":78},\"main\",{\"_79\":80,\"_81\":82},\"src\",\"/static/images/logos/Hme_logo_black.png\",\"alt\",\"black\",\"android\",{\"_87\":91,\"_89\":92},\"ios\",{\"_87\":88,\"_89\":90},\"icon_src\",\"https://www.healthifyme.com/in/images/Appstore.svg\",\"href\",\"https://apps.apple.com/in/app/healthifyme-weight-loss-plan/id943712366\",\"https://www.healthifyme.com/in/images/Playstore.svg\",\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.healthifyme.basic\u0026hl=en_IN\u0026gl=US\",\"title\",\"HealthifyMe provides smart meal plans personalized by our expert nutritionists and customized workout plans with our certified fitness coaches. HealthifyMe enables you to track your daily calorie intake, weight goals, workouts, hand washing tracker, water consumed, sleep monitoring, meal journal \u0026 step counter. Accelerate your fitness goals to a whole new level.\",\"image\",\"https://www.healthifyme.com/in/images/HelathifyMe-Logo-White.svg\",\"url\",\"https://healthifyme.com\",{\"_9\":330,\"_11\":331,\"_332\":333,\"_13\":334,\"_335\":333,\"_15\":336,\"_17\":336,\"_110\":220,\"_19\":337,\"_113\":251,\"_31\":338,\"_29\":30,\"_116\":339},{\"_9\":288,\"_11\":289,\"_13\":290,\"_15\":291,\"_17\":292,\"_110\":183,\"_19\":293,\"_113\":114,\"_31\":294,\"_29\":30,\"_116\":114},{\"_9\":244,\"_11\":245,\"_13\":246,\"_15\":247,\"_17\":248,\"_110\":117,\"_19\":249,\"_113\":114,\"_31\":250,\"_29\":30,\"_116\":251},{\"_9\":212,\"_11\":213,\"_13\":214,\"_15\":215,\"_17\":216,\"_110\":217,\"_19\":218,\"_113\":114,\"_31\":219,\"_29\":30,\"_116\":220},{\"_9\":175,\"_11\":176,\"_13\":177,\"_15\":178,\"_17\":179,\"_110\":180,\"_19\":181,\"_113\":114,\"_31\":182,\"_29\":30,\"_116\":183},{\"_9\":105,\"_11\":106,\"_13\":107,\"_15\":108,\"_17\":109,\"_110\":111,\"_19\":112,\"_113\":114,\"_31\":115,\"_29\":30,\"_116\":117},{\"_173\":174},{\"_171\":172},{\"_171\":172},\"tesimonials-v1\",\"basic testimonials\",\"section_type\",8,[168,169,170],\"variant\",1,{\"_93\":118,\"_119\":120,\"_121\":122,\"_123\":124},\"sort\",5,\"Join the Health Revolution. It’s Time.\",\"subtitle\",\"Find your reason to Healthify and bring the change that you’ve always aimed for.\",\"stats\",[146,147,148,149],\"testimonials\",[125,126,127],{\"_15\":141,\"_95\":142,\"_130\":143,\"_132\":144},{\"_15\":136,\"_95\":137,\"_130\":138,\"_132\":139},{\"_15\":128,\"_95\":129,\"_130\":131,\"_132\":133},\"Priyanka Jain\",{\"_134\":135,\"_81\":128},\"tagline\",\"I Healthified to be an active mom.\",\"feedback\",\"Supported by HealthifyMe’s personal coaches, customized diet plans, calorie counters, Priyanka lost 15 Kg post-pregnancy.\",\"path\",\"/static/images/home_website/landing/assets/Priyanka.png\",\"Dr. Rashi Manocha\",{\"_134\":140,\"_81\":136},\"I Healthified to realise my dreams\",\"Supported by HealthifyMe’s personal coaches, customized diet plans, calorie counters, Dr. Rashi won over her PCOS and lost 18 Kg in 12 months.\",\"/static/images/home_website/landing/assets/Rashi.png\",\"Krishan Thukral\",{\"_134\":145,\"_81\":141},\"I Healthified from 94 to 80 Kg to play with my son.\",\"With the HealthifyMe app, Krishan lost 14 Kg and is now his son’s favourite.\",\"/static/images/home_website/landing/assets/Krishan.png\",{\"_150\":164,\"_152\":165},{\"_150\":160,\"_152\":161},{\"_150\":156,\"_152\":157},{\"_150\":151,\"_152\":153},\"icon\",{\"_134\":154,\"_81\":155},\"label\",\"Editors’ Choice\",\"/static/images/home_website/landing/icons/Editors Choice.svg\",\"Editors choice\",{\"_134\":158,\"_81\":159},\"Kg Weight Lost\",\"/static/images/home_website/landing/icons/Weight Lost.svg\",\"weight lost\",{\"_134\":162,\"_81\":163},\"Rated\",\"/static/images/home_website/landing/icons/Rating.svg\",\"rating\",{\"_134\":166,\"_81\":167},\"Users\",\"/static/images/home_website/landing/icons/Users.svg\",\"users\",\"IN\",\"USA\",\"UK\",\"$date\",\"2022-06-23T09:19:05.372Z\",\"$oid\",\"62b430095ae30bb6543752c5\",{\"_173\":211},{\"_171\":210},{\"_171\":210},\"insights-v1\",\"basic insights\",7,[168,169,170,209],{\"_93\":184,\"_119\":185,\"_186\":187},4,\"Improved Tools. Better Insights.\",\"Track detailed body and health metrics with cutting-edge technology.\",\"cardsLayout\",[188,189,190],{\"_93\":205,\"_119\":206,\"_95\":207},[195,196],{\"_93\":191,\"_119\":192,\"_95\":193},\"Timeline \u0026 History\",\"Get a feed of your whole day in one single place and receive feedback on your choices.\",{\"_134\":194,\"_81\":191},\"/static/images/home_website/landing/assets/Timeline+History.png\",{\"_93\":201,\"_119\":202,\"_95\":203},{\"_93\":197,\"_119\":198,\"_95\":199},\"Body Metrics\",\"Don't just lose weight, lose the right kind of weight. Get detailed body metrics.\",{\"_134\":200,\"_81\":191},\"/static/images/home_website/landing/assets/Body+Metrics.png\",\"Food Tracker\",\"Log meals with a touch, check your macros, or simply take a photo of your meal.\",{\"_134\":204,\"_81\":191},\"/static/images/home_website/landing/assets/Food+Tracker.png\",\"Continuous Glucose Monitoring\",\"Track your glucose response to food \u0026 activity and learn what works for you.\",{\"_134\":208,\"_81\":191},\"/static/images/home_website/landing/assets/Glucose+Monitoring.png\",\"SEA\",\"2022-06-17T08:25:40.534Z\",\"62ac3a840475e15e9d3640cd\",{\"_173\":243},{\"_171\":242},{\"_171\":242},\"features-v1\",\"basic features\",6,[168,169,170],{\"_93\":221,\"_119\":222,\"_223\":224,\"_225\":226},3,\"Diet Flexibility and Fitness Freedom\",\"With the right data, reach your fitness goals faster, get personalized coaching and work with greater efficiency.\",\"cardsLayoutPrimary\",[235,236],\"cardsLayoutSecondary\",[227,228],{\"_95\":232},{\"_95\":229},{\"_134\":230,\"_81\":231},\"/static/images/home_website/landing/generic/Lifestyle4.png\",\"icon image 2\",{\"_134\":233,\"_81\":234},\"/static/images/home_website/landing/assets/Lifestyle_gray.png\",\" icon image\",{\"_95\":240},{\"_95\":237},{\"_134\":238,\"_81\":239},\"/static/images/home_website/landing/assets/Lifestyle2_update.png\",\" icon image 2\",{\"_134\":241,\"_81\":234},\"/static/images/home_website/landing/generic/Lifestyle1.png\",\"2022-06-17T08:25:06.965Z\",\"62ac3a620475e15e9d3640cc\",{\"_173\":287},{\"_171\":286},{\"_171\":286},\"pro-v1\",\"basic pro\",[168],{\"_93\":252,\"_119\":253,\"_254\":255,\"_186\":256},2,\"Healthify with Pro. Like a Pro.\",\"Make accurate progress powered by 360° guidance.\",\"cta\",[281],[257,258,259,260],{\"_93\":276,\"_119\":277,\"_95\":278},{\"_93\":271,\"_119\":272,\"_95\":273},{\"_93\":266,\"_119\":267,\"_95\":268},{\"_93\":261,\"_119\":262,\"_95\":263},\"Metabolic Panel\",\"A dashboard with 80+ key metabolic parameters that helps you stay healthy \u0026 identify underlying medical conditions.\",{\"_134\":264,\"_81\":265},\"/static/images/home_website/landing/assets/Metabolic.png\",\"lab tests for 80+ parameters\",\"Smart Scale\",\"Smart in every way, the Smart Scale breaks down body weight into body fat, muscle mass, protein, hydration and bone mass. So you lose the right kind of weight.\",{\"_134\":269,\"_81\":270},\"/static/images/home_website/landing/assets/Smart+Scale_update.png\",\"A weighing Scale with feautres to measure body fat, muscle mass, protein and bone mass\",\"Pro Coaches\",\"Pro Coaches gather insights from Pro CGM, Smart Scale, Pro Tracker \u0026 Metabolic Panel to give you personalised guidance in real time.\",{\"_134\":274,\"_81\":275},\"/static/images/home_website/landing/assets/Pro-Coaches-Gradient.png\",\"Two Coaches Standing Side by Side\",\"CGM\",\"Small yet powerful, the CGM helps you lose weight more consistently. It tracks your glucose every minute. So you know what to eat and when to burn.\",{\"_134\":279,\"_81\":280},\"/static/images/home_website/landing/assets/Bios_gray.png\",\"continuous glucose monitoring device\",{\"_89\":282,\"_152\":283,\"_284\":285},\"https://www.healthifyme.com/pro/\",\"Know More\",\"id\",\"pro-cta-1\",\"2022-06-17T08:24:24.814Z\",\"62ac3a380475e15e9d3640cb\",{\"_173\":329},{\"_171\":328},{\"_171\":328},\"offerings-v1\",\"basic offerings\",[168,169,170],{\"_93\":295,\"_119\":296,\"_223\":297,\"_225\":298},\" A Connected Fitness Ecosystem\",\"Improve your health holistically, more consistently and experience change like never before.\",[313,314],[299,300,301],{\"_93\":261,\"_119\":262,\"_150\":311},{\"_93\":307,\"_119\":308,\"_150\":309},{\"_93\":302,\"_119\":303,\"_150\":304},\"Better Health Insights\",\"Detailed insights to keep you on track and help you improve your health regimen.\",{\"_134\":305,\"_81\":306},\"/static/images/home_website/landing/icons/Insights.svg\",\"Glucose Monitoring\",\"Personalized Fitness Plans\",\"Extensive Diet and Workout Plans customized for you and your fitness goals.\",{\"_134\":310,\"_81\":306},\"/static/images/home_website/landing/icons/Plans.svg\",{\"_134\":312,\"_81\":306},\"/static/images/home_website/landing/icons/Metabolic.svg\",{\"_93\":321,\"_119\":322,\"_150\":323,\"_95\":324},{\"_93\":315,\"_119\":316,\"_150\":317,\"_95\":318},\"Elite Coaches\",\"Best-in-class Coaches for supreme guidance and motivation.\",{\"_134\":320,\"_81\":306},{\"_134\":319,\"_81\":315},\"/static/images/home_website/landing/assets/Elite--Coaches.png\",\"/static/images/home_website/landing/icons/Coaches.svg\",\"Better Tech. Better Health.\",\"A connec